      <div class="table-container">
        <h3>Smoothed Year-by-Year Growth Projection</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">This table illustrates what your balance would look like each year if it grew steadily at the calculated CAGR, assuming no intermediate deposits, withdrawals, or volatility.</p>
